253
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,840
Tristan Rot.

254
00:15:55,400 --> 00:15:56,840
Tristan Rot?

255
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,640
Er wollte meinen Schlüssel haben.

256
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:01,440
Tristan Rot
wollte Ihren Schlüssel zum Innenhof?

257
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,520
